msgid "Before proceeding, physically mark the Reference Point"
msgstr "继续前，请在舞台上用可见标记标出参考点和四个网格角（胶带等）。"

msgid "Click a corner or use Tab to select it, then use arrow keys to nudge"
msgstr "点击角点或按 Tab 选择，然后用方向键微调"

msgid "Diagonal"
msgstr "对角线"

msgid "Dimensions and position of the rectangular tracking area"
msgstr "矩形追踪区域的尺寸与位置"

msgid "Drag each corner marker to the corresponding physical mark on the stage"
msgstr "将各角点标记拖到舞台上对应的物理标记处"

msgid "Drag each corner to its physical stage mark for precise calibration"
msgstr "将各角点拖到对应的舞台物理标记，精确标定"

msgid "Drag the crosshair marker to the physical Reference Point mark visible on the stage."
msgstr "将十字准星拖到舞台上可见的参考点标记处。"

msgid "Drag the crosshair to the physical Reference Point mark"
msgstr "将十字准星拖到物理参考点标记处"

msgid "Enter the horizontal FOV from your camera datasheet, or pick your sensor size and focal length and we will compute it."
msgstr "输入相机说明上的水平 FOV，或选择传感器尺寸和焦距后系统自动计算。"

msgid "Enter the width and depth of the rectangular tracking area you marked on stage."
msgstr "输入舞台上标记的矩形追踪区域的宽度和深度。"

msgid "If your corners are invalid, three things could be wrong"
msgstr "如果角点无效，可能是以下三种情况之一"

msgid "Load Defaults"
msgstr "加载默认值"

msgid "Measure between the marks you placed on stage. Precision matters"
msgstr "请测量舞台上标记之间的距离，精度至关重要"

msgid "No video feed available. Values below are still valid, but the visual review is unavailable."
msgstr "无视频信号。以下数值仍然有效，但无法进行可视化检查。"

msgid "Physical camera position and orientation relative to the Reference Point"
msgstr "相机相对于参考点的物理位置与方向"

msgid "Restore Last"
msgstr "恢复上次"

msgid "Review"
msgstr "审核"

msgid "Select and configure the camera input"
msgstr "选择并配置相机输入"

msgid "Start with the two downstage corners (front), then adjust the upstage corners (back)."
msgstr "先从两个下台口角点（前方）开始，然后调整上台口角点（后方）。"

msgid "Take your time with accurate markings"
msgstr "精确标记决定最终标定精度，请耐心操作"

msgid "Understand the setup and prepare the physical space"
msgstr "了解设置流程并准备物理空间"

msgid "Verify all values before applying"
msgstr "应用前确认所有数值"

msgid "Verify your grid is rectangular: measure both diagonals on stage"
msgstr "验证网格为矩形：测量舞台上两条对角线"

msgid "Zoom in on your browser (Ctrl/Cmd + scroll) for more precision."
msgstr "在浏览器中放大（Ctrl/Cmd + 滚轮）可获得更高精度。"

msgid "Reference Point:"
msgstr "参考点："

msgid "All measurements in this wizard are relative to a single Reference Point. This should be the same reference point for all show control systems that you plan to connect to OpenFollow. If your venue has a defined origin point, you should use that. If you do not have an existing reference point, we recommend the"
msgstr "本向导中的所有测量均相对于单一参考点。所有接入的演出控制系统应共用同一参考点。若场地已有定义的原点，请使用它。如无现有参考点，建议使用"

msgid "center of the stage front edge"
msgstr "舞台前缘中点"

msgid "as the default."
msgstr "作为默认值。"

msgid "The Grid:"
msgstr "网格："

msgid "The grid area must be a"
msgstr "网格区域必须是一个"

msgid "right-angled rectangle"
msgstr "直角矩形"

msgid "as large as possible that lies flat on the main performance level. All four corners must be"
msgstr "尽可能大且平放于主表演面。四个角必须"

msgid "clearly visible in the camera feed"
msgstr "在摄像头画面中清晰可见"

msgid "Do not worry, you can follow performers outside this grid, as long as they are in the area visible to the camera."
msgstr "无需担心，表演者走到网格外仍可追踪，只要他们在摄像头可见区域内。"

msgid "the precision of the final calibration depends on them."
msgstr "最终标定精度取决于标记的准确性。"

msgid "Define where the Reference Point sits within the grid. By default, it is at the center of the front edge (X Offset = 0, Y Offset = depth / 2)."
msgstr "定义参考点在网格中的位置。默认位于前缘中点（X 偏移 = 0，Y 偏移 = 深度 / 2）。"

msgid "even 10cm off will affect tracking accuracy. Spacing controls the visual grid density (does not affect calibration). If your Reference Point is 1m left of the grid center: set X Offset = -1."
msgstr "即使 10cm 的偏差也会影响追踪精度。间距只控制网格显示密度（不影响标定）。如果参考点在网格中心左侧 1m，则设 X 偏移 = -1。"

msgid "The change applies live – the new pipeline starts within ~1 s of saving."
msgstr "修改即时生效 — 保存后约 1 秒内启动新的采集管线。"

msgid "Enter the camera physical position relative to the Reference Point, in"
msgstr "输入相机相对于参考点的物理位置，单位"

msgid "These use PSN theatrical coordinates: X = stage left, Y = upstage, Z = up."
msgstr "使用 PSN 剧场坐标系：X = 舞台左，Y = 上台口方向，Z = 向上。"

msgid "Enter the camera angle. If the camera points straight at the stage, start with Pitch approx -30 degrees (looking down), Yaw = 0 degrees, Roll = 0 degrees."
msgstr "输入相机角度。如果相机正对舞台，起始值建议：俯仰 ≈ -30°（向下看），偏航 = 0°，横滚 = 0°。"

msgid "All corners move together with the reference point to roughly align the overlay with your stage."
msgstr "所有角点随参考点一起移动，使叠加层大致对齐舞台。"

msgid "You can also click the crosshair and use arrow keys to nudge it precisely (hold Shift for larger steps)."
msgstr "也可以点击十字准星后使用方向键精确微调（按住 Shift 键大步移动）。"

msgid "The labels mark image quadrants: DSL goes on the front mark at the left of the image, DSR on the front mark at the right, and so on. (Note: with a front-of-house camera the left of the image is stage right.)"
msgstr "标签标示画面区域：DSL 放画面左侧前方标记，DSR 放右侧前方标记，以此类推。（注意：FOH 摄像机位时，画面左侧 = 舞台右侧。）"

msgid "If a corner turns red, the shape is invalid."
msgstr "若角点变红，表示形状无效。"

msgid "No video feed available. Configure a video source in Step 3, then return here and press"
msgstr "无视频信号。请在步骤 3 中配置视频源，然后返回此处并点击"

msgid "Pitch must be between -0.5 degrees and -90 degrees"
msgstr "俯仰必须介于 -0.5° 到 -90° 之间"

msgid "for larger steps)."
msgstr "大步移动）。"

msgid "Choose the video input that matches your camera setup. The change applies live - the new pipeline starts within ~1 s of saving."
msgstr "选择匹配您相机设置的视频输入。修改即时生效 — 保存后约 1 秒内启动新的采集管线。"

msgid "If your corners are invalid, three things could be wrong: The position of your camera relative to the reference point, your marked rectangle has not the same size as the grid, or the corners of your rectangle are not 90 degrees."
msgstr "如果角点无效，可能是以下三种情况之一：相机相对参考点的位置有误、标记的矩形与网格尺寸不符、矩形的角不是直角。"

msgid "Click a corner or use Tab to select it, then use arrow keys to nudge (hold Shift for larger steps)."
msgstr "点击角点或按 Tab 选中，然后用方向键微调（按住 Shift 大步移动）。"

msgid "For pixel-precise placement, click Fine adjust to switch to a 4x-zoomed per-corner view."
msgstr "如需像素级精确放置，点击\"精细调整\"切换到 4 倍放大逐角视图。"

msgid "Before proceeding, physically mark the Reference Point and the four grid corners on the stage with visible markers, so they are easily visible on camera (tape, gaffer marks, etc.)."
msgstr "继续前，请在舞台上用可见标记标示参考点和四个网格角（胶带等），确保在摄像头中清晰可见。"

msgid "Drag each corner marker to its physical mark on the stage. The labels are stage positions: DSL/USL are stage left, DSR/USR are stage right (D = downstage/front, U = upstage/back). With a front-of-house camera you see the audience view, so stage left is on the right of the image (audience right) and stage right is on the left (audience left)."
msgstr "从相机视角出发，将各角点标记拖到舞台上对应的物理标记处。标签标示画面区域：DSL 放画面左侧前方标记，DSR 放右侧前方标记，以此类推。（注意：FOH 摄像机位时，画面左侧即为舞台右侧。）"

msgid "Drag the crosshair marker to the physical Reference Point mark visible on the stage. All corners move together with the reference point to roughly align the overlay with your stage."
msgstr "将十字准星拖到舞台上可见的参考点标记处。所有角点随参考点一起移动，使叠加层大致对齐舞台。"

msgid "Measure between the marks you placed on stage. Precision matters - even 10cm off will affect tracking accuracy. Spacing controls the visual grid density (does not affect calibration). If your Reference Point is 1m left of the grid center: set X Offset = -1."
msgstr "测量舞台上标记之间的距离，精度至关重要——即使 10cm 偏差也会影响追踪精度。间距只控制网格显示密度（不影响标定）。若参考点在网格中心左侧 1m，设 X 偏移 = -1。"

msgid "Take your time with accurate markings - the precision of the final calibration depends on them."
msgstr "精确标记决定最终标定精度，请耐心操作。"

msgid "Verify your grid is rectangular: measure both diagonals on stage - they must be equal. The expected diagonal is shown above."
msgstr "验证网格为矩形：测量舞台上两条对角线，两者必须相等。预期对角线见上方。"

msgid "Zoom in on your browser (Ctrl/Cmd + scroll) for more precision. You can also click the crosshair and use arrow keys to nudge it precisely (hold Shift for larger steps)."
msgstr "在浏览器中放大（Ctrl/Cmd + 滚轮）可获得更高精度。也可以点击十字准星后使用方向键精确微调（按住 Shift 大步移动）。"

msgid "Start with the two downstage corners (front), then adjust the upstage corners (back). If a corner turns red, the shape is invalid. For pixel-precise placement, click"
msgstr "先从两个下台口角点（前方）开始，然后调整上台口角点（后方）。若角点变红表示形状无效。如需像素级精确放置，点击"

msgid "to switch to a 4x-zoomed per-corner view."
msgstr "切换到 4 倍放大逐角视图。"

msgid "NDI® Source"
msgstr "NDI® 源"
